snippet.title: Space War: Infinity [STEAM TRAILER]
snippet.description:
Space War: Infinity is a semi-procedural shoot-'em-up with a weapon upgrade system of the ship and unlocking of items. Embark in your ship and fight for your survival!

Game page:
https://www.risingmoongames.com/our-games/space-war-infinity
